args: Barbecue's all loaded up to go, too!\nGrillmaster Ranzal's gonna open y'all\na portal to the meat dimension!
Going on vacation, I take it?
Aren't you going to join us, Alex?\nIt's sure to be a good time.
I... I'm just not sure I have any business\ncavorting around like that.
You're not that girl who used to live in the\ndarkness anymore. Show yourself grace.
I think I WILL go and have some summer\nfun with you all this year.
(Elisanne's right. I'm not who I used to be.\nSurely I can loosen up at least a little.)
(Here's to a fun-filled getaway with my\ndear friend—the one who pulled me back\ninto the light!)
However... Something else awaited Alex\non the sun-kissed sands of the beach.
I saw you, Alex! You were AMAZING!
(Hrk... So much for a relaxing trip!)
(I guess that incident brought down\na little too much attention...)
A contest that Verica once participated in,\nto be specific.
That's right. It's a pageant of sorts to\ndetermine whose beauty rivals that of\nthe sea itself.

I won't be joining in this time around, but I
figured I might know some of the entrants.
When I went to say hello, though, I could
tell something was amiss.
Evidently, one of the people running the\nevent suddenly took ill, and now they're\nshorthanded.
I wish I could help, but my schedule is\nfull up with my fortune-telling work.
I see. I'd be happy to pitch in, then.
So all I need to do is distribute ballots to\neach spectator, and then collect them?\nSounds simple enough.

And now, at long last, we come to the
climactic finale of our grand contest!
Dear spectators and distinguished lookers-
on, are your ballots ready?!
Time to get to work.\n...Everyone, you can just hand\nyour ballots to me, and—
Aaaaagh! There're fiends coming from the\nocean!
Tch. Couldn't finish it off with just my\nself-defense knife.
But if one strike isn't enough...then I'll\nland another! Hrah! Yah! Hiiiyah!
Ladies and gentlemen, are you seeing\nthis?! A staffer of this very contest has\ngallantly laid low the aquatic menace!
Uh... Why's there so much commotion?
As elegant as a swan...if swans carried\nknives! She fought with grace and\nsplendor, leaving us all utterly bewitched!
Thank you, Alex! The contest is saved\nbecause of you!
Oh, er... I didn't do anything special.

Now, then! With the heat of enthusiasm
still burning in our hearts, we continue our
contest! Everyone, if you would be so kind
as to prepare your votes?
Now I can finally do my job. Everyone,\nplease hand me your ballots.
You're amazing! Team Alex all the way!
Since when do I have a fan club?!
At long last, vote tabulation is COMPLETE!\nAnd now, the news you've ALL been\nwaiting for.
Why, what's this?! The honored first-place\nwinner of our contest this year iiiiis...

You certainly did not, but the people have
spoken! The sight of you bravely facing off
against evil was a spectacle worthy of our
great contest!

Well then, how about this?
We'll treat the second-place winner as
the champion, and confer a special bonus
prize to the illustrious Alex!
This is all happening so fast.
I'm turning red from all these people\nstaring at me...
You're quite the local celebrity, Alex.
Can't say I'm enjoying it. I've never been\nin the spotlight quite like this before.
Ain't no wonder. For an assassin who lived\nher life lurkin' in the shadows, this kinda\nheat must be unbearable.
Hey, Alex! Can I have your autograph?
Hrk... I'm sorry! I can't take this anymore!
(How am I supposed to deal with all this?)
(So much for my peaceful vacation\nwith Elisanne...)
